HEADWORD: Jeremiade
<hw>Jer`e*mi"ade</hw> }</mhw>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <etsep>Jeremiah</etsep>, the prophet: cf. F.
<ets>j⟦eacute⟧r⟦eacute⟧miade</ets>.]</ety> <def>A tale of sorrow,
